item.title: Prayer bpn6208 in Marshallese
item.description: O ao Anij! O ao Anij! Emol, dri jerbal rein Am rej oktak waj nan Kwe, bukot jiban jen ailin in tiriamo eo Am. Emol, Am kwojarjar emoj an kinor waj ir im emoj air urur kin kijeek in yokwe eo Am, bukot kejramon jen ailin eo Am ekabwilonlon, ilo air kejetdrikdrik bwe renaj bed ilo ailin eo Am ilan. Emol, elab air kijoror in bok kejramon eo ej itok jen Kwe, ilo air konan bok meran jen al in mol.
